strings: <voice_0x01001299><se_high>Accuracy: After defeating the stone wizard and wielding the wand, I can't say what to think.
<voice_0x0100129A><se_high>Accuracy: That's what I want to say, but I don't think I'm going to avenge my brother's death.
<voice_0x0100129B><se_high>Accuracy: We don't know who this Lord Lapthorne is, or who he is. However, it cannot be said that the rod was not found.
<voice_0x0100129C><se_high>Accuracy: I will not stop searching until I find the wand key and the open Tree of Wrath.
<voice_0x0100129F><se_high>Accuracy: Hello, at least it's not weird! Sometimes you need to look in the mirror.
<voice_0x010012A0><se_high>Accuracy: disposition? Thank you very much <hero> I know you are beautiful.
